## Testing Pyramid Adherence (testing_pyramid.rule)

- Development for all user stories must prioritize a strong testing pyramid.
- Before implementing end-to-end UI tests (e.g., Behat), ensure that underlying logic, business rules, and component interactions are thoroughly covered by unit tests (e.g., PHPUnit) and integration tests (e.g., PHPUnit with a framework-specific test harness like the WordPress Test Harness).
- Behat tests should primarily focus on user flows, acceptance criteria verification from a user perspective, and visual confirmation once core functionality is verified at lower levels. 